  "texts": [
    "In Sect. 5, we describe the imaging procedure and investigate the primary image morphologies.",
    "We reconstruct the images using a variety of imaging techniques, ranging from traditional inverse imaging to Bayesian posterior exploration.",
    "We compare the recovered image structure across the different imaging meth-ods, frequency bands, calibration pipelines, and observing dates.",
    "We recover a clear ring-like structure, with a deep central depression and a diameter of ∼42 µas.",
    "We also find that the position angle of the brightest region of the ring is between 200 • and 230 •, which is different from the position angle measured in 2017."
